      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は私の定期検診に付き添ってくれて\nありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for coming\nwith my regular checkups today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.366666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの健康状態を把握しておくのも\nマネージャーの務めだからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Keeping track of our idols’ health is\npart of the manager’s job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.033333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "また普段の私の様子を知ってる人から話を聞きたいって\n先生からも言われていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My doctor was saying she wanted to hear from people who\nknow how I’m doing daily.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "だから{user}さんに付き添ってもらえて\nよかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it was good I could get you\nto come along with me‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2733333110809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
