      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 30.466666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、これで次のライブに向けて練習に専念出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ now I can really focus on rehearsing for our next live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それは頼もしいが……\nもしかして、何か悩みがあるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good of you‚ but…\nare you sure there’s nothing bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 42.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！　ど、どうしてですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? W-why do you ask?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 45.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "最近のさくらは時々表情が暗くなるから\n何かに悩んでいるのかと思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ you’ve been wearing this dark expression‚\nso I thought maybe you had something on your mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、{user}さんはよく見てますね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It figures‚ {user}-san‚ you were watching closely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 57.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "実はサニピの次のライブで気になることがあるんです\n今度の会場の東京レイーズって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing is‚ I am worried about the next Sunny Peace live.\nThe next venue is Tokyo Reyes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 62.4666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈さんがたった一年でLizNoirの\n記録を塗り替えて満員にした会場ですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the venue where Mana-san beats LizNoir’s record\nby filling it in just a year‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 73.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "その日のことはよく覚えてるよ\nあの時の麻奈は体調が万全とは言えなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I remember that day well.\nMana wasn’t at her best physically that day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、応援してくれるファンの期待に\n麻奈は最高のパフォーマンスで応えたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ she met the fans’ expectations by\ndelivering her best performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 86.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですか……\nみんなの期待に応える麻奈さんはやっぱり凄いです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s how it was…\nTypical amazing Mana-san‚ living up to everyone’s expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "……すずちゃんや雫ちゃんが言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan and Shizuku-chan were saying that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 93.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "東京レイーズでの麻奈さんのライブは\n伝説になるような素晴らしいライブだったって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-san’s show at Tokyo Reyes was so amazing\nthat it’s legendary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
