      "text": "サニピが麻奈さんを超える伝説のライブを見せるとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Will Sunny Peace show us a performance to surpass Mana-san’s?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリ決勝を超える\nライブになるんじゃないかとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Will the show surpass the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix finals?”\nand so on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 126.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
