      "text": "私達への期待が日に日に高まっているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Expectations on us are rising day by day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばスタッフさんも、麻奈のライブに負けまいと\n気合いを入れてセットや小道具に趣向を凝らしているよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it‚ the staff are determined not to be outdone\nby Mana’s show‚ so they’re coming up with fancy sets and props.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 137.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
